snippet.title: The Download: Git 2.52, Gemini 3, a private file converter & more
snippet.description:
This week on The Download, Cassidy covers the release of Git 2.52 and its new "jetpack" feature for checking file history. We also dive into the launch of Google's Gemini 3 Pro model in GitHub Copilot and Microsoft's new Agent 365 for the enterprise. Plus, we spotlight VERT, a privacy-focused open source file converter.

#Git #GitHub #Gemini #OpenSource

— CHAPTERS — 

00:00 Welcome to The Download
00:25 Git 2.52 and the new last-modified command
01:09 Gemini 3 Pro lands in Copilot
01:38 Microsoft announces Agent 365
02:01 Project spotlight: VERT file converter
02:32 This week's news recap

---

Links:

Git 2.52 is here:
https://github.blog/open-source/git/highlights-from-git-2-52/

Gemini 3 Pro:
https://venturebeat.com/ai/google-unveils-gemini-3-claiming-the-lead-in-math-science-multimodal-and

Microsoft Agent 365:
https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-agent-365/overview
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SzxwdNeSnKs

Open source project:
https://github.com/VERT-sh/VERT
